@199@^GAS - Steeda^@^GAS - Steeda^@199@^http://www.steeda.com/classic-design-concepts-mustang-sequential-taillights-96-04-067-102022b/^@^Steeda^@^Classic Design Concepts Mustang Sequential Taillights (96-04)^@^http://www.steeda.com/images/thumbnails/530/530/detailed/5/classic-design-concepts-mustang-sequential-taillights-96-04-067-102022b(3).jpg; http://www.steeda.com/images/thumbnails/530/530/detailed/5/classic-design-concepts-mustang-sequential-taillights-96-04-067-102022b(2).jpg; http://www.steeda.com/images/thumbnails/530/530/detailed/5/classic-design-concepts-mustang-sequential-taillights-96-04-067-102022b.jpg^@^067-102022b^@^<p>First introduced in the '60s the Ford Mustang featured three-lens sequential taillights which not only caught people's attention but also gave new life to the average blinker. It was not until 2010 that sequential taillights once again became a factory option on new models. Bring your '96-'04 Mustang up to speed and give the rear end a classic touch with the CDC Sequential Taillights. </p> <p>Direct plug and play. This Sequential Taillight System requires no splicing resulting in a high tech lighting system for your rear end that installs effortlessly in minutes. </p> <p>This advanced engineered system uses brand new harnesses and sockets with a pre-programmed microprocessor that controls timing for optimum performance. It has been moisture tested and cycle tested for quality results. </p> <p>Standard with reverse circuit protection and voltage regulation this tail light system is physically sealed to protect the electronics from any moisture. When the brake is applied the lights will sequence once and then remain illuminated until the brake pedal is released. </p> <p>This kit will also work on all 1994-1995 Mustangs equipped with 1996-1998 style tail lights. </p> <p><strong>Note: </strong> Will not fit 1999-2001 SVT Cobras </p> <p><strong>Product Benefits</strong> </p> <ul> <li>Sequences rear turn and brake lights from inboard to outboard</li> <li>Direct plug and play</li> <li>Manufactures limited lifetime warranty</li> </ul><p>Time to install: <strong>About 30 Minutes</strong></p><p>Level of difficulty: <strong>Easy</strong></p><p>Tools needed: <strong>Basic Tools</strong></p><p>Model year(s): <strong>2004 2003 2002 2001 2000 1999 1998 1997 1996</strong></p><p>Model(s): <strong>All</strong></p><p>Transmission(s): <strong>Manual Automatic</strong></p>^@^Mustang^@^ All ^@^Mustang Electric^@^2004 2003 2002 2001 2000 1999 1998 1997 1996 ^@^Mustang Lighting^@^19.95^
