@234@^GAS - Steeda^@^GAS - Steeda^@234@^http://www.steeda.com/koni-2005-2010-mustang-str-t-strut-279-8750-1030/^@^Steeda^@^Koni Mustang STR.T Street Strut - Front - 05-10^@^http://www.steeda.com/images/thumbnails/530/362/detailed/1/279-8750-1030.jpg^@^279-8750-1030^@^<p>Koni STR.T shocks and struts are high performance non adjustable dampers that are designed to be a perfect complement to lowering springs but also make an ideal service replacement and upgrade to stock ride height cars with factory original shocks and struts. <br /> <br /> These Koni STR.T shock and strut units are a direct bolt on non adjustable twin tube high pressure gas design that will enhance both ride quality and handling performance. <br /> <br /> All Koni STR.T units come with a lifetime warranty against manufacturing defects. <br /> <br /> <strong>Note:</strong> Koni STR.T shocks and struts are sold and priced individually. 2 struts and 2 shocks make a full set. Koni STR.T units are NOT adjustable.<br /> <br /> <strong>Product Benefits</strong> </p> <ul> <li>Twin-tube high pressure gas design</li> <li>Direct bolt-on replacement</li> <li>Lifetime Warranty</li> </ul><p>Time to install: <strong>About 4 Hours</strong></p><p>Level of difficulty: <strong>Tech Recommended</strong></p><p>Tools needed: <strong>Shop Tools</strong></p><p>Model year(s): <strong>2010 2009 2008 2007 2006 2005</strong></p><p>Model(s): <strong>Bullitt GT V6 GT500</strong></p><p>Transmission(s): <strong>Manual Automatic</strong></p>^@^Mustang^@^ Bullitt GT V6 GT500 ^@^Mustang Suspension^@^2010 2009 2008 2007 2006 2005 ^@^Mustang Shocks & Struts^@^169.95^
@235@^GAS - Steeda^@^GAS - Steeda^@235@^http://www.steeda.com/koni-shelby-gt500-sport-series-strut-279-8241-1494sport/^@^Steeda^@^Koni Mustang Sport Series Strut - Front (11-14 GT500)^@^http://www.steeda.com/images/thumbnails/530/362/detailed/1/279-8241-1494sport.jpg^@^279-8241-1494SPORT^@^<p>Koni Sport &quot;Yellows&quot; are a Koni's original and still the best premium adjustable shock and strut unit they offer. </p> <p>Koni Sport Yellows feature an external adjustment right at the top of the unit for rebound adjustment. This adjustment allows you to soften the ride for daily driving or firm it up for handling performance and track use. Adjustment is done on the car by simply using the provided knob to turn the adjuster clockwise to soften the ride or counter clock wise to stiffen the ride. </p> <p>These shock and strut units are a direct bolt on twin tube high pressure gas design that will enhance both ride quality and handling performance. </p> <p>All Koni Sport Yellow units come with a lifetime warranty against manufacturing defects. </p> <p><strong>Note:</strong> Koni Sport Yellow shocks and struts are sold and priced individually. 2 struts and 2 shocks make a full set. Koni Yellow units are adjustable for rebound only. </p> <p><strong>Product Benefits</strong> </p> <ul> <li>Big handling improvements</li> <li>Best KONI shock for all lowering springs</li> <li>External rebound adjustment</li> <li>Lifetime Warranty</li> </ul><p>Time to install: <strong>About 4 Hours</strong></p><p>Level of difficulty: <strong>Tech Recommended</strong></p><p>Tools needed: <strong>Shop Tools</strong></p><p>Model year(s): <strong>2014 2013 2012 2011</strong></p><p>Model(s): <strong>GT500</strong></p><p>Transmission(s): <strong>Manual</strong></p>^@^Mustang^@^ GT500 ^@^Mustang Suspension^@^2014 2013 2012 2011 ^@^Mustang Shocks & Struts^@^269.95^
