@351@^GAS - Steeda^@^GAS - Steeda^@351@^http://www.steeda.com/cdc-05-09-mustang-rear-decklid-panel-067-110904/^@^Steeda^@^CDC Mustang Rear Decklid Panel (05-09)^@^http://www.steeda.com/images/thumbnails/530/362/detailed/2/067-110904.jpg; http://www.steeda.com/images/thumbnails/530/362/detailed/2/067-110904-1.jpg^@^067-110904^@^<p>Classic Design Concepts Rear Decklid Blackout Panel really cleans up the rear of your Mustang and greatly improves it's appearance. </p> <p>This ABS panel easily installs with high strength double sided adhesive tape. No drilling or painting required. It neatly cleans up the style of the rear end by blacking out the entire decklid and eliminating the rear OE center badge. </p> <p>In addition the rectangular space between the taillights of the '05-'09 models lies indented just a little over an inch. This trim panel fills that gap completely so the deck lid and taillights all work together nicely for a much cleaner look. Regardless of your Mustang's color the addition of the Deck Lid Trim Panel is sure to get your vehicle more attention. </p> <p>Available plain or with the GT logo. </p> <p><strong>Product Benefits</strong> </p> <ul> <li>Fill is gap between tail lights</li> <li>Blackout look improves vehicle apprearace</li> <li>Eliminates false gas door trunk badge</li> <li>High Quality ABS Construction</li> <li>No drilling or painting required</li> </ul><p>Time to install: <strong>About 15 Minutes</strong></p><p>Level of difficulty: <strong>Easy</strong></p><p>Tools needed: <strong>Basic Tools</strong></p><p>Model year(s): <strong>2009 2008 2007 2006 2005</strong></p><p>Model(s): <strong>Bullitt GT V6 GT500</strong></p><p>Transmission(s): <strong>Manual Automatic</strong></p>^@^Mustang^@^ Bullitt GT V6 GT500 ^@^Mustang Body Kits^@^2009 2008 2007 2006 2005 ^@^Mustang Grills & Inserts^@^179.95^
