@353@^GAS - Steeda^@^GAS - Steeda^@353@^http://www.steeda.com/classic-design-concepts-mustang-rear-deck-lid-panel-067-1011-7005-01/^@^Steeda^@^Classic Design Concepts Mustang Rear Deck Lid Panel (10-14 All)^@^http://www.steeda.com/images/thumbnails/530/362/detailed/4/1_vw7d-wq.jpg; http://www.steeda.com/images/thumbnails/530/362/detailed/4/2_q33x-jw.jpg; http://www.steeda.com/images/thumbnails/530/362/detailed/4/3_gzxu-1m.jpg^@^067-1011-7005-01^@^<p>Add retro styling to your 2010-2014 Mustang with a Classic Design Concepts (CDC) Deck Lid Trim Panel. This Rear Tail Light Panel will give your Mustang's deck lid the same classic look as the Muscle Mustangs of yesteryear and it deletes the fake rear gas cap for a cleaner appearance. </p> <p>The Classic Design Concepts deck lid panel is injection molded from OE quality material for a perfect fit and features a unique ribbed design with a grained texture. </p> <p>No drilling or messy bondo is required for installation. This CDC Rear Deck Lid Trim Panel installs easily with the supplied doubled sided 3M automotive bonding tape for a quick and simple installation. </p> <p>Please note: The Classic Design Concepts Rear Deck Lid Panel fits perfectly on all 2010-2014 Mustangs including the V6 GT and Shelby GT500 models. </p> <p><strong>Product Benefits</strong> </p> <ul> <li><span style=background-color: initial

