@388@^GAS - Steeda^@^GAS - Steeda^@388@^http://www.steeda.com/ford-racing-mustang-dash-gauge-pod-05-14-161-m-6304gpod-a/^@^Steeda^@^Ford Racing Mustang Dash Gauge Pod (05-14)^@^http://www.steeda.com/images/thumbnails/530/362/detailed/7/ford-racing-mustang-dash-gauge-pod-05-14-161-m-6304gpod-a.jpg^@^161-M-6304GPACK-MA^@^<p>Keep track of your investment with some gauges installed to a Ford Racing Mustang Gauge Pod. This Ford Racing BOSS Gauge Pack came as original equipment on the Special Edition Laguna Seca BOSS Mustang. </p> <p><strong>Please Note: </strong>Gauges are not included. </p> <p><strong>Product Benefits</strong> </p> <ul> <li>Fits 2005-2014 Mustang GT Shelby GT500 and Mustang V6</li> <li>Gauge pod accepts 3 standard 2-1/16 inch gauges</li> <li>Includes dash mounting bracket</li> </ul><p>Time to install: <strong>About 2 Hours</strong></p><p>Level of difficulty: <strong>Tech Recommended</strong></p><p>Tools needed: <strong>Basic Tools</strong></p><p>Model year(s): <strong>2014 2013 2012 2011 2010 2009 2008 2007 2006 2005</strong></p><p>Model(s): <strong>GT V6 GT500</strong></p><p>Transmission(s): <strong>Manual Automatic</strong></p>^@^Mustang^@^ GT V6 GT500 ^@^Mustang Accessories^@^2014 2013 2012 2011 2010 2009 2008 2007 2006 2005 ^@^Mustang Gauge Mounting Pods^@^59.95^
@391@^GAS - Steeda^@^GAS - Steeda^@391@^http://www.steeda.com/steeda-mustang-whipple-supercharger-belt-drive-555-3350-pol/^@^Steeda^@^Steeda Mustang Whipple Supercharger Belt Drive - 15-17 PSI/Polished Snout (05-10)^@^http://www.steeda.com/images/thumbnails/530/362/detailed/1/555-3350-pol.jpg; http://www.steeda.com/images/thumbnails/530/362/detailed/3/555-3350-pol-1.jpg; http://www.steeda.com/images/thumbnails/530/362/detailed/3/555-3350-pol-2.jpg; http://www.steeda.com/images/thumbnails/530/362/detailed/3/555-3350-pol-3.jpg; http://www.steeda.com/images/thumbnails/530/362/detailed/3/555-3350-pol-4.jpg^@^555-3350-POL^@^<p>Tired of belts slipping breaking or simply being thrown off your Whipple supercharged Mustang when pushing it to the limit? Those days are now over! Steeda’s Belt Drive System for Whipple Supercharger was designed to prevent any such belt problems that are all too common during competition or just hardcore use of your Mustang. </p> <p>Steeda designed this belt drive package to relocate the supercharger drive off the factory 6-rib system making it a dedicated 10-rib belt system which drives the supercharger and nothing else. Removing the supercharger drive from the primary accessory drive serves to eliminate any and all slippage problems that can occur including both on the initial tip in and under full load. The standard accessories are driven by a Steeda underdrive pulley for even more power and reduced accessory load. </p> <p>Our 10-rib system is available in boost levels of approximately 11psi to 17psi on a Gen 1 Whipple system and approximately 13 to 19psi on a Gen 2 Whipple system with no slippage under any conditions and no throwing or breakage of the supercharger belt. </p> <p>The package includes a new supercharger snout billet pulleys billet mounting plates 2 new belts and a heavy-duty belt tensioner. Although we recommend a Steeda hood it only takes a minor modification to fit the system under your stock hood. Full installation instructions including to the procedure for measuring stock hood clearance are included. </p> <p>Already own a Steeda Belt Drive and want to change boost levels? Take a look at our separate lower boost pulley kits. </p> <p><span class=BodyRedBold"><strong>Important Note</strong>:</span> Stated boost levels are estimates only based on GEN 2 Whipple superchargers and will vary widely depending on numerous factors including but not limited to: Exhaust configuration cylinder heads port configuration camshafts geographic elevation engine compression throttle body size boost gauge accuracy and other factors beyond the control of Steeda Autosports. Use numbers provided for guidance only. In general cars with large cams cylinder heads etc will have slightly lower boost levels.<span style="color: #ff0000

