@495@^GAS - Steeda^@^GAS - Steeda^@495@^http://www.steeda.com/magnaflow-mustang-gt-competition-cat-back-exhaust-2015-263-191101/^@^Steeda^@^Magnaflow Mustang GT Competition Cat-Back Exhaust (2015)^@^http://www.steeda.com/images/thumbnails/530/362/detailed/6/magnaflow-mustang-gt-competition-cat-back-exhaust-2015-263-191101.jpg; http://www.steeda.com/images/thumbnails/530/362/detailed/6/magnaflow-mustang-gt-competition-cat-back-exhaust-2015-263-191101(2).jpg^@^263-19101^@^<p>*In stock and ready to ship!* </p> <div> Magnaflow brings sound energy to the next level to produce the lightest and highest horsepower exhaust system available today! </div> <p>Give your new 2015 Mustang GT an aggressive race inspired sound with Magnaflow's Cat-Back Exhaust. This Magnaflow Cat-Back Exhaust is made in the USA with 3&quot; Stainless Mandrel-Bent piping with fully welded constructed round mufflers for strength and performance. Heads will turn when the thunderous sound of the exhaust escapes the dual split rear 4 1/2&quot; polished stainless steel tips. </p> <p>This Magnaflow Cat-Back Exhaust come complete with all hardware needed and will fit precisely around the new independent suspension on the 2015 Mustang GT. </p> <p><strong>Product Benefits</strong> </p> <ul> <li>Over 30 rwhp and 30 ft/lbs tq increase compared to stock!</li> <li>30 lbs lighter than factory exhaust!</li> <li>409 stainless steel construction straight-through flow design</li> <li>No cabin drone or resonance while driving</li> <li>Smooth deep tone with over 100-decibel sound rating from outside the car</li> <li>Aggressive muscle car sound</li> <li>3&quot; mandrel bent stainless steel tubing</li> <li>4.5&quot; polished tips</li> <li>Lifetime construction warranty</li> </ul><p>Time to install: <strong>About 1 1/2 Hours</strong></p><p>Level of difficulty: <strong>Tech Recommended</strong></p><p>Tools needed: <strong>Basic Tools</strong></p><p>Model year(s): <strong>2015</strong></p><p>Model(s): <strong>GT</strong></p><p>Transmission(s): <strong>Manual Automatic</strong></p>^@^Mustang^@^ GT ^@^Mustang Exhaust^@^2015 ^@^Mustang Cat-Back Exhaust^@^1410.95^
@496@^GAS - Steeda^@^GAS - Steeda^@496@^http://www.steeda.com/magnaflow-mustang-ceramic-shorty-headers-263-700028/^@^Steeda^@^Magnaflow Mustang Ceramic Shorty Headers (11-14 GT)^@^http://www.steeda.com/images/thumbnails/530/362/detailed/5/700028.jpg^@^263-700028^@^<p>Magnaflow Stainless Steel 1-3/4&quot; Ceramic Coated Shorty Headers for 2011 2012 2013 and 2014 Mustang GTs and 2012-2013 Boss 302s. </p> <p>Replace your restrictive factory exhaust manifold with a set of 2011-2014 GT/Boss 302 Mustang shorty headers from Magnaflow. With improved horsepower and exhaust tone these ceramic coated stainless steel shorty headers are perfect for anyone looking to get a little more power out of their coyote. </p> <p>These Magnaflow shorty headers are constructed from 16 gauge Mandrel bent Stainless Steel and then coated with a long lasting Titanium finish Ceramic Coat. Designed to be a direct bolt in replacement for your factory stock exhaust manifolds the 3/8&quot; thick CNC flange will bolt right up to the head of your GT/Boss providing a good solid seal with no worries of leaks or warping due to heat. </p> <p><strong>Product Benefits</strong> </p> <ul> <li><span style=background-color: initial

