@498@^GAS - Steeda^@^GAS - Steeda^@498@^http://www.steeda.com/magnaflow-mustang-exhaust-263-15151/^@^Steeda^@^Magnaflow Mustang Axle-Back Exhaust (13-14 GT)^@^http://www.steeda.com/images/thumbnails/530/362/detailed/2/263-15151.jpg^@^263-15151^@^<p>From simple axle back exhaust systems to full cat back systems which include over axle piping with mandrel bent tubing Magnaflow has what you need. </p> <p>Street Magnaflow systems feature 3&quot; pipes with an oval muffler and a 4 inch tip. Magnaflow Street systems will increase sound slightly from stock without excessive sound levels when combined with the stock headers and catalytic converters. With header systems and high flow cat systems Magnaflow Street Systems come alive with sound but never become overly loud with an muscular tone that is sure to please without intrusive sound or resonance inside the vehicle. </p> <p>Magnaflow Competition systems feature a round style muffler with 4&quot; inch tip. Magnaflow Competition systems feature a substantially more aggressive sound than street Magnaflow systems. Want people to know you are coming? Magnaflow Competition systems are the way to go. </p> <p>Available in Cat Back and Axle Back configurations. </p> <p><strong>Product Benefits</strong> </p> <ul> <li>Choice of sound levels (street vs competition) </li> <li>Quality stainless steel construction </li> <li>Available in Axle Back or Full Cat Back Configurations </li> <li>Limited lifetime warranty </li> <li>Increased horsepower and torque </li> </ul><p>Time to install: <strong>About 1 1/2 Hours</strong></p><p>Level of difficulty: <strong>Tech Recommended</strong></p><p>Tools needed: <strong>Basic Tools</span> </div> </div> <div style=with:100%

