@584@^GAS - Steeda^@^GAS - Steeda^@584@^http://www.steeda.com/3d-carbon-mustang-fender-vents-023-691618/^@^Steeda^@^3D Carbon Mustang Fender Vents - 10-14^@^http://www.steeda.com/images/thumbnails/530/362/detailed/1/023-691618.jpg; http://www.steeda.com/images/thumbnails/530/362/detailed/2/023-691618-1.jpg; http://www.steeda.com/images/thumbnails/530/362/detailed/2/023-691618-2.jpg^@^023-691618^@^<p>3dCarbon's Functional Fender Vents enhance the existing body lines with aggressive race car styling and and provide functional flow through heat extraction helping to cool under hood temperatures. </p> <p>These fender vents are manufactured from high quality urethane and include 3M automotive adhesive mounting tape for installation. Painting required. Kit includes driver and passenger side vents. </p> <p><strong>Product Benefits</strong> </p> <ul> <li>Fully functional heat extractors</li> <li>Quality urethane construction</li> <li>Aggressive modern styling</li> </ul><p>Time to install: <strong>About 4 Hours</strong></p><p>Level of difficulty: <strong>Tech Recommended</strong></p><p>Tools needed: <strong>Shop Tools</strong></p><p>Model year(s): <strong>2014 2013 2012 2011 2010</strong></p><p>Model(s): <strong>GT V6 GT500 Boss</strong></p><p>Transmission(s): <strong>Manual Automatic</strong></p>^@^Mustang^@^ GT V6 GT500 Boss ^@^Mustang Body Kits^@^2014 2013 2012 2011 2010 ^@^Mustang Louvers^@^279.95^
@585@^GAS - Steeda^@^GAS - Steeda^@585@^http://www.steeda.com/3d-carbon-05-09-mustang-ducktail-spoiler-023-691016/^@^Steeda^@^3D Carbon Mustang Ducktail Spoiler - 05-09^@^http://www.steeda.com/images/thumbnails/530/362/detailed/2/023-691016.jpg^@^023-691021^@^<p>The 3 Piece Rear Duck Tail spoiler is manufactured in High Pressure polyurethane and attaches to the deck lid and quarter panels. No screws or hole drilling is required. The spoiler attaches with OE approved 3M Double Face Tape. </p> <p>The 3 Piece spoiler can be installed on Mustangs with the Factory GT Spoiler. The width of the 3 Piece spoiler from front to rear is enough to cover the 4 –Holes from the factory spoiler. </p> <p><strong>Product Benefits</strong> </p> <ul> <li>Very easy to install</li> <li>No drilling required</li> </ul><p>Time to install: <strong>About 1 Hour</strong></p><p>Level of difficulty: <strong>Easy</strong></p><p>Tools needed: <strong>Basic Tools</strong></p><p>Model year(s): <strong>2009 2008 2007 2006 2005</strong></p><p>Model(s): <strong>Bullitt GT V6 GT500</strong></p><p>Transmission(s): <strong>Manual Automatic</strong></p>^@^Mustang^@^ Bullitt GT V6 GT500 ^@^Mustang Body Kits^@^2009 2008 2007 2006 2005 ^@^Mustang Rear Wings^@^349.95^
@586@^GAS - Steeda^@^GAS - Steeda^@586@^http://www.steeda.com/3d-carbon-mustang-rear-spoiler-023-691604/^@^Steeda^@^3D Carbon 3D500 Mustang Rear Spoiler - (10-14)^@^http://www.steeda.com/images/thumbnails/530/362/detailed/2/023-691604.jpg; http://www.steeda.com/images/thumbnails/530/362/detailed/2/023-691604-1.jpg; http://www.steeda.com/images/thumbnails/530/362/detailed/2/023-691604-2.jpg^@^023-691604^@^<p>This rear spoiler from 3D Carbon is gives your 2010 and newer Mustang an aggressive look with easy installation. Constructed from blow molded composite plastic it required minimum prep work before painting and is a direct bolt on in place of the factory Mustang rear spoiler. </p> <p><strong>Product Benefits</strong> </p> <ul> <li>Direct bolt on installation</li> <li>Aggressive styling</li> <li>Easy prep and paint</li> </ul><p>Time to install: <strong>About 1 Hour</strong></p><p>Level of difficulty: <strong>Easy</strong></p><p>Tools needed: <strong>Basic Tools</strong></p><p>Model year(s): <strong>2014 2013 2012 2011 2010</strong></p><p>Model(s): <strong>GT V6 GT500 Boss</strong></p><p>Transmission(s): <strong>Manual Automatic</strong></p>^@^Mustang^@^ GT V6 GT500 Boss ^@^Mustang Body Kits^@^2014 2013 2012 2011 2010 ^@^Mustang Rear Wings^@^279.95^
@587@^GAS - Steeda^@^GAS - Steeda^@587@^http://www.steeda.com/3d-carbon-05-09-mustang-rear-valance-023-691025/^@^Steeda^@^3D Carbon Mustang Rear Valance (05-09)^@^http://www.steeda.com/images/thumbnails/530/362/detailed/2/023-691025.jpg^@^023-691025^@^<p>Most people just cut a hole in the factory rear bumper cover after converting to a dual exhaust system which looks horrible and is not going to win any car shows. But a 3dCarbon Rear Valance Skirt will give your Pony a clean finished appearance that will have people guessing if you made any changes at all. </p> <p>The 3dCarbon V6 Rear Valance Skirt is manufactured to higher than OEM specifications from high-pressure injected molded polyurethane material for its flexibility durability and for a perfect fit. </p> <p>The 3dCarbon valance attaches directly to the factory V6 bumper via screws in the wheel wells and 3M automotive grade bonding tape around the perimeter. Installation will require trimming a hole for the driver side exhaust tip in the stock factory rear bumper before installing the 3dCarbon Rear Valance Skirt. </p> <p><strong>Product Benefits</strong> </p> <ul> <li>Easy to install</li> <li>No tools required</li> </ul><p>Time to install: <strong>About 15 Minutes</strong></p><p>Level of difficulty: <strong>Easy</strong></p><p>Tools needed: <strong>Basic Tools</strong></p><p>Model year(s): <strong>2009 2008 2007 2006 2005</strong></p><p>Model(s): <strong>Bullitt GT V6 GT500</strong></p><p>Transmission(s): <strong>Manual Automatic</strong></p>^@^Mustang^@^ Bullitt GT V6 GT500 ^@^Mustang Body Kits^@^2009 2008 2007 2006 2005 ^@^Mustang Fascias & Body Kits^@^299.95^
