@761@^GAS - Steeda^@^GAS - Steeda^@761@^http://www.steeda.com/afco-mustang-dual-fan-heat-exchanger-417-80280-pro/^@^Steeda^@^AFCO Dual Fan Mustang Heat Exchanger - 05-14^@^http://www.steeda.com/images/thumbnails/530/362/detailed/2/417-80280-pro.jpg^@^417-80280-PRO^@^<p>AFCO's Aluminum Double Pass Pro Series Heat Exchanger for the Shelby GT500 unlocks the full power potential of your Shelby GT500. This new unit greatly increases the cooling area over the stock unit for effective cooling of the supercharged intercooler system. The AFCO Double Pass Heat Exchanger features high flow twin SPAL Hi-CFM fans to maintain airflow over the cooler when the vehicle is not moving. </p> <p>Combine the large surface area and fans for constant airflow and you have outstanding water to air heat exchanger upgrade over the stock unit. </p> <p>Complete “true” bolt on kit includes all necessary hardware wiring harnesses and color instruction manual for simple installation. No modifications to the vehicle are required. This is a true bolt on for the Shelby GT500. </p> <p><strong>Note:</strong> Please check fitments listed before for your application. </p> <p><strong>Specifications</strong> </p> <ul> <li>Height 11.35” (fin cover to fin cover)</li> <li>Width 26 3/8” (tank to tank)</li> <li>Tank Thickness 2.25”</li> <li>Core Thickness 1.5”</li> <li>Core Width 22 3/8”</li> </ul> <p><strong>Product Benefits</strong> </p> <ul> <li>Complete “true” bolt on kit includes all necessary hardware wiring harnesses</li> <li>This new unit increases the cooling area over the stock unit by more</li> <li>Dual fans for maximum cooling</li> </ul><p>Time to install: <strong>About 4 1/2 Hours</strong></p><p>Level of difficulty: <strong>Tech Recommended</strong></p><p>Tools needed: <strong>Basic Tools</strong></p><p>Model year(s): <strong>2014 2013 2012 2011 2010 2009 2008 2007 2006 2005</strong></p><p>Model(s): <strong>GT GT500</strong></p><p>Transmission(s): <strong>Manual Automatic</strong></p>^@^Mustang^@^ GT GT500 ^@^Mustang Cooling^@^2014 2013 2012 2011 2010 2009 2008 2007 2006 2005 ^@^Mustang Heat Exchangers^@^888.95^
