@775@^GAS - Steeda^@^GAS - Steeda^@775@^http://www.steeda.com/ford-racing-mustang-rear-quad-exhaust-161-m-5230-msvtcd/^@^Steeda^@^Ford Racing Mustang Quad Tip Axle-Back & Lower Rear Valance (13-14 GT)^@^http://www.steeda.com/images/thumbnails/530/362/detailed/1/161-m-5230-msvtcd.jpg^@^161-M-5230-MSVTCD^@^<p>Love the 13-14 GT500 quad tip exhaust look? You can now have it for your Mustang GT! This Ford Racing kit includes awesome sounding quad tip 13-14 GT500 O.E. mufflers and a 13-14 GT500 rear lower valance for a complete finished installation. </p> <p>Mufflers are 409 stainless steel with polished 304 stainless tips. </p> <p><strong>Note:</strong> Shelby rear valance requires some cutting of O.E. valance for fitment. </p> <p><strong>Product Benefits</strong> </p> <ul> <li>Awesome throaty sound</li> <li>Add quad tip GT500 style to your Mustang GT</li> <li>Includes mufflers rear valance and hardware</li> </ul><p>Time to install: <strong>About 3 1/2 Hours</strong></p><p>Level of difficulty: <strong>Tech Recommended</strong></p><p>Tools needed: <strong>Basic Tools</strong></p><p>Model year(s): <strong>2014 2013</strong></p><p>Model(s): <strong>GT</strong></p><p>Transmission(s): <strong>Manual Automatic</strong></p>^@^Mustang^@^ GT ^@^Mustang Exhaust^@^2014 2013 ^@^Mustang Axle-Back Exhaust^@^099.95^
@776@^GAS - Steeda^@^GAS - Steeda^@776@^http://www.steeda.com/ford-racing-coyotae-mustang-crate-engine-161-m-6007-m50/^@^Steeda^@^Ford Racing Mustang 5.0L Ti-VCT Crate Engine^@^http://www.steeda.com/images/thumbnails/530/362/detailed/2/161-m-6007-m50.jpg^@^161-M-6007-M50^@^<p>Ford Racing's all-aluminum 5.0L Mustang crate engine is a modern 5.0L 32-valve DOHC V-8 that uses advanced features like Twin Independent Variable Camshaft Timing (Ti-VCT) to deliver 412+ horsepower @ 6500 rpm and 390 ft.-lb.+ of torque @ 4250 rpm (with premium fuel). The lightweight aluminum cylinder block features cross-bolted main bearing caps and thick main bearing bulkheads for bottom-end strength. Optimized oil drainback and windage control improve high-rpm performance. </p> <p>Direct replacement for 2011-2012 Mustangs. It is also a popular re-trofit upgrade as well. </p> <p>Vehicle harness and PCM are NOT included regardless of application. For retrofit applications use of Ford Racing's NEW wiring PCM and installation kit M-6017-A504V is required. Engine is fully assembled except for alternator. For alternator use alternator kit see M-8600-M50BALT </p> <p>Engine features a light weight aluminum block with forged steel crankshaft forged steel connecting rods and cast aluminum pistons. </p> <p><strong>Product Benefits</strong> </p> <ul> <li>Direct fit on 2011-12 Mustang GT's</li> <li>Popular retrofit for other applications</li> <li>Light weight aluminum engine</li> <li412 li="></li412> </ul><p>Time to install: <strong>About 20 Hours</strong></p><p>Level of difficulty: <strong>Tech Required</strong></p><p>Tools needed: <strong>Shop Tools</strong></p><p>Model year(s): <strong>2014 2013 2012 2011 2010 2009 2008 2007 2006 2005 2004 2003 2002 2001 2000 1999 1998 1997 1996</strong></p><p>Model(s): <strong>GT</strong></p><p>Transmission(s): <strong>Manual Automatic</strong></p>^@^Mustang^@^ GT ^@^Mustang Engine^@^2014 2013 2012 2011 2010 2009 2008 2007 2006 2005 2004 2003 2002 2001 2000 1999 1998 1997 1996 ^@^Mustang Heads & Blocks^@^8.95^
@777@^GAS - Steeda^@^GAS - Steeda^@777@^http://www.steeda.com/ford-racing-mustang-hood-pins-161-m-16700-a/^@^Steeda^@^Ford Racing Stainless Steel Mustang Hood Pins - 79-04^@^http://www.steeda.com/images/thumbnails/530/362/detailed/2/161-m-16700-a.jpg; http://www.steeda.com/images/thumbnails/530/362/detailed/3/161-m-16700-a-1.jpg^@^161-M-16700-A^@^<p>Look fast even when you're sitting still! Add piece-of-mind and secure your hood with these high quality Stainless Steel Hood Pins. Recommended for high speed driving and all fiberglass hoods. Ask Steeda's technical experts for some easy installation tips when you order. </p> <p><strong>Product Benefits</strong> </p> <ul> <li>Secure fitting</li> <li>Easy to use</li> </ul><p>Time to install: <strong>About 1 Hour</strong></p><p>Level of difficulty: <strong>Easy</strong></p><p>Tools needed: <strong>Basic Tools</strong></p><p>Model year(s): <strong>2004 2003 2002 2001 2000 1999 1998 1997 1996 1995 1994 1993 1992 1991 1990 1989 1988 1987 1986 1985 1984 1983 1982 1981 1980 1979</strong></p><p>Model(s): <strong>5.0L V8 Bullitt Cobra Cobra R Mach 1 GT V6 2.3L</strong></p><p>Transmission(s): <strong>Manual Automatic</strong></p>^@^Mustang^@^ 5.0L V8 Bullitt Cobra Cobra R Mach 1 GT V6 2.3L ^@^Mustang Body Kits^@^2004 2003 2002 2001 2000 1999 1998 1997 1996 1995 1994 1993 1992 1991 1990 1989 1988 1987 1986 1985 1984 1983 1982 1981 1980 1979 ^@^Mustang Hood Accessories^@54.95
@778@^GAS - Steeda^@^GAS - Steeda^@778@^http://www.steeda.com/ford-racing-mustang-recaro-race-seats-161-m-63660005-mc/^@^Steeda^@^Ford Racing Mustang Recaro Race Seats - Pair (Late 12-14)^@^http://www.steeda.com/images/thumbnails/530/362/detailed/5/m63660005mc.jpg; http://www.steeda.com/images/thumbnails/530/362/detailed/5/M-63660005-MB-2.jpg^@^161-M-63660005-MC^@^<p>Similar to OEM seats found in the 2012 Boss 302 Laguna Seca these race seats are equipped with an integrated headrest seat belt pass through openings enhanced bolstered shoulder back and thigh areas to keep you securely in place during spirited driving and nice and comfortable during daily driving. </p> <p>These race seats are manufactured especially for Ford Racing by Recaro using an extremely high grade breathable dark gray cloth that has been strategically reinforced to protect high wear areas from abuse. Also these seats can be fully reclined. </p> <p>These Ford Racing seats look and feel great they also help keep you safe in the event of an accident with side air bags integrated into their design. Power wiring harness and seat tracks are included for side air bag functionality. </p> <p>This pair of Ford Racing Recaro Race Seats are designed as a direct bolt-in replacement for all Late 2012 to 2014 Mustangs including the V6 GT Boss and Shelby GT500 models. </p> <p>Please note: Does not fit 2011-Mid 2012 Mustangs as Ford changed the style of air bag connector mid model year. </p><p>Time to install: <strong>About 2 1/2 Hours</strong></p><p>Level of difficulty: <strong>Tech Recommended</strong></p><p>Tools needed: <strong>Basic Tools</strong></p><p>Model year(s): <strong>2014 2013 2012</strong></p><p>Model(s): <strong>5.0L GT V6 GT500 Boss</strong></p><p>Transmission(s): <strong>Manual Automatic</strong></p>^@^Mustang^@^ 5.0L GT V6 GT500 Boss ^@^Mustang Dress Up^@^2014 2013 2012 ^@^Mustang Seats^@^999.95^
@779@^GAS - Steeda^@^GAS - Steeda^@779@^http://www.steeda.com/ford-racing-gt500-oe-brembo-brake-kit-161-m-2300-t/^@^Steeda^@^Ford Racing GT500 OE Brembo Brake Kit (05-14)^@^http://www.steeda.com/images/thumbnails/530/362/detailed/4/M-2300-T.jpg^@^161-M-2300-T^@^<p>The 2013-14 Shelby GT500 is arguably the pinnacle of Mustang engineering to date. Part of that marvel is the awesome brake setup Ford graced it with. The engineers at Ford Racing did their homework and released the FRPP M-2300-T Brake Kit allowing you to bring your 2005-2014 GT 2012-13 Boss 302 and 2007-12 GT500 up to original equipment 2013-2014 Shelby braking specs. </p> <p>This front and rear Ford Racing brake upgrade kit includes massive six-piston Brembo calipers mated to 15 inch Brembo front rotors. The front calipers are gloss black powdercoated with white Brembo lettering. Rear calipers are single piston GT500 paired with huge 13.8 inch rotors. </p> <p>Please note: a 19 inch wheel is required for brake clearance. New axle mounting flanges are required for this rear brake upgrade so be sure and grab our <a href=http://www.steeda.com/steeda-mustang-finned-differential-cover-fill-drain-plugs-555-8142/" target="_blank">finned differential cover with drain/fill plugs</a> and a couple of quarts of Royal Purple gear oil. Because you'll need to bleed your brakes be sure to also have plenty of Motorcraft Brake Fluid on hand as well. </p> <p><strong>Product Benefits</strong> </p> <ul> <li><span style="background-color: initial

