@780@^GAS - Steeda^@^GAS - Steeda^@780@^http://www.steeda.com/ford-racing-gt500-twin-throttle-body-161-m-9926-cj65/^@^Steeda^@^Ford Racing 65mm GT500 Throttle Body (07-14 GT500)^@^http://www.steeda.com/images/thumbnails/530/362/detailed/2/161-m-9926-cj65.jpg^@^161-M-9926-CJ65^@^<p>Ford Racing's twin 65 mm billet throttle body is a direct bolt on in the factory location. </p> <p>Features precision machined billet aluminum construction and gorgeous polished finish with Ford Racing logo. Throttle body comes fully assembled including throttle position sensor and actuator motor. </p> <p>Recommended on high horsepower naturally aspirated engines with custom tuning and supercharged applications. Not recommended for stock engine and stock engine calibration. Custom tuning required for proper performance/drivability. </p> <p><strong>Product Benefits</strong> </p> <ul> <li>Precision billet machined construction</li> <li>Comes complete including TPS and actuator motor</li> <li>Direct bolt on!</li> </ul><p>Time to install: <strong>About 30 Minutes</strong></p><p>Level of difficulty: <strong>Easy</strong></p><p>Tools needed: <strong>Basic Tools</strong></p><p>Model year(s): <strong>2014 2013 2012 2011 2010 2009 2008 2007</strong></p><p>Model(s): <strong>GT500</strong></p><p>Transmission(s): <strong>Manual</strong></p>^@^Mustang^@^ GT500 ^@^Mustang Induction^@^2014 2013 2012 2011 2010 2009 2008 2007 ^@^Mustang Throttle Bodies^@^789.95^
@781@^GAS - Steeda^@^GAS - Steeda^@781@^http://www.steeda.com/ford-racing-mustang-jounce-bumper-kit-161-m-5570-a/^@^Steeda^@^Ford Racing Mustang Jounce Bumper Kit (05-14 All)^@^http://www.steeda.com/images/thumbnails/530/362/detailed/4/M-5570-A.jpg^@^161-M-5570-A^@^<p>These Ford Racing Jounce Stops are the same exact ones found as standard original equipment on the 2012-2014 Shelby GT500 Mustang. </p> <p>These GT500 Jounce Bumper Stops may look like your stock ones but the difference is that they are much softer/spongier than stock. So when the jounce bumpers compress they release slower than stock to provide a less violent chassis reaction when the vehicle bounces off them. This improves stability and ride comfort when used in conjunction with FRPP lowering springs. </p> <p>This Ford Racing Jounce Bumper Kit contains two front jounce stop bumpers and two rear jounce stop bumpers. </p> <p>When you're adding suspension parts to your ride you can't go wrong by installing parts from the people that know it best. Ford Racing's legendary quality ensures a perfect fit and years of hassle-free use. </p> <p>This set of four Ford Racing Jounce Bumper Stops fits all 2005 to 2014 Mustangs with Ford Racing Lowering Springs installed including the V6 GT Bullitt Boss and Shelby GT500 models. </p> <p>Also note - compatible with the following Ford Racing spring kits; M5300K M5300L M5300N M5300P. </p> <p><strong> Product Benefits</strong> </p> <ul> <li><span style=background-color: initial

