@840@^GAS - Steeda^@^GAS - Steeda^@840@^http://www.steeda.com/mgp-red-mustang-caliper-covers-w-pony-tri-bar-logo-front-and-rear-05-10-gt-v6-228-10197smb1rd/^@^Steeda^@^MGP Red Mustang Caliper Covers w/ Pony Tri-Bar Logo - Front & Rear (05-10 GT V6)^@^http://www.steeda.com/images/thumbnails/530/362/detailed/5/1_zn9r-pw.jpg; http://www.steeda.com/images/thumbnails/530/362/detailed/5/F2MB1RD.jpg; http://www.steeda.com/images/thumbnails/530/362/detailed/5/R3MB1RD.jpg^@^228-10197SMB1RD^@^<p>MGP Caliper Covers are a great way to set off your rims and tires. They feature the iconic &quot;Tri-Bar Pony&quot; emblem on the rear covers with &quot;Mustang&quot;lettering on the fronts and are Officially Licensed by Ford. </p> <p>MGP Caliper Covers are manufactured in the USA with 6061-T6 aerospace grade aluminum. They are TIG welded for strength powder-coated for durability and include a patented stainless steel fastening system. No adhesive tape or caliper modifications are required. </p> <p>MGP Mustang Caliper Covers not only look fantastic but they also act as a protective dust shield to help keep your rims looking cleaner longer. </p> <p>Designed to fit over the factory brakes this set of four MGP caliper covers include all the required hardware needed for installation on the 2005 to 2010 GT and V6 Mustangs. Does not fit Shelby GT500 BOSS 302 or Brembo equipped GT models. </p> <p><strong>Product Benefits</strong> </p> <ul> <li>Race ready looks</li> <li>Reduces brake dust so rims stay clean</li> <li>Easy installation</li> <li>17&quot; wheel minimum</li> </ul><p>Time to install: <strong>About 1 Hour</strong></p><p>Level of difficulty: <strong>Easy</strong></p><p>Tools needed: <strong>No Tools</strong></p><p>Model year(s): <strong>2014 2013 2012 2011</strong></p><p>Model(s): <strong>GT V6</strong></p><p>Transmission(s): <strong>Manual Automatic</strong></p>^@^Mustang^@^ GT V6 ^@^Mustang Brakes^@^2014 2013 2012 2011 ^@^Mustang Brake Caliper Covers^@^239.95^
@841@^GAS - Steeda^@^GAS - Steeda^@841@^http://www.steeda.com/mgp-mustang-caliper-covers-carbon-fiber-w-gt-logo-front-and-rear-228-10095smg1cf/^@^Steeda^@^MGP Mustang Caliper Covers - Carbon Fiber w/ GT Logo - Front & Rear (94-04 GT V6)^@^http://www.steeda.com/images/thumbnails/530/362/detailed/5/1_pclg-pg.jpg; http://www.steeda.com/images/thumbnails/530/362/detailed/5/front.jpg; http://www.steeda.com/images/thumbnails/530/362/detailed/5/rear.jpg^@^228-10095SMG1CF^@^<p>This set of four Carbon Fiber Style MGP Caliper Covers are a great way to set off your new rims and they feature modern &quot;Mustang&quot; lettering on the front two covers and the &quot;GT&quot; logo on the rear two. </p> <p>MGP makes their Caliper covers using light weight 6061-T6 Aerospace Aluminum that is formed to the caliper for a perfect fit. They are then finished in a Carbon Fiber appearance using a Hydrofilm process. The installation brackets are TIG welded in place for extra security. </p> <p>MGP Mustang Caliper Covers not only look amazing but they also act as a protective dust shield to help keep your rims looking cleaner longer. </p> <p>Designed to fit over the factory brakes this set of four MGP caliper covers include all the required hardware needed for fast and easy installation on 1994 to 2004 Mustangs including the V6 and GT models. </p> <p><strong>Note:</strong> Due to the Hydrofilm process additional lead time may be required. </p> <p><strong>Product Benefits</strong> </p> <ul> <li><span style=background-color: initial

