@846@^GAS - Steeda^@^GAS - Steeda^@846@^http://www.steeda.com/ford-racing-touring-catback-mustang-exhaust-black-tips-2015-161-m-5200-m8tb/^@^Steeda^@^Ford Racing Touring Catback Mustang Exhaust-Black Tips (2015)^@^http://www.steeda.com/images/thumbnails/530/362/detailed/6/ford-racing-touring-catback-mustang-exhaust-black-tips-2015-161-m-5200-m8tb(1).jpg; http://www.steeda.com/images/thumbnails/530/326/detailed/6/M-5230-M8SConcars_mi6n-7l.jpg^@^161-M-5200-M8TB^@^<p>Take your 2015 Mustang GT to the next level with the Ford Racing Cat-back Exhaust. </p> <p>This exhaust system is 30 lbs lighter than the factory system with its 2.5&quot; mandrel bent stainless steel piping. Of course once the starter twists the powerful Coyote 5.0L to life you will delight in the deep and aggressive race car sound. </p> <p>The Ford Racing exhaust is a direct bolt on system and exits in the factory locations with two 4&quot; black tips that will compliment the rear bumper. </p> <p><strong>Please Note: </strong>This Ford Racing Sport Cat-back Exhaust System is 49 state drive by noise legal not intended for use in the state of California. </p> <p><strong>Product Benefits</strong> </p> <ul> <li>Aggressive muscle car sound</li> <li>Direct bolt on fit</li> <li>4&quot; black painted tips</li> </ul><p>Time to install: <strong>About 2 1/2 Hours</strong></p><p>Level of difficulty: <strong>Tech Recommended</strong></p><p>Tools needed: <strong>Basic Tools</strong></p><p>Model year(s): <strong>2015</strong></p><p>Model(s): <strong>GT</strong></p><p>Transmission(s): <strong>Manual Automatic</strong></p>^@^Mustang^@^ GT ^@^Mustang Exhaust^@^2015 ^@^Mustang Cat-Back Exhaust^@^1599.95^
@847@^GAS - Steeda^@^GAS - Steeda^@847@^http://www.steeda.com/ford-racing-sport-mustang-ecoboost-axle-back-exhaust-chrome-tips-2015-161-m-5230-m4sc/^@^Steeda^@^Ford Racing Sport Mustang EcoBoost Axle-back Exhaust Chrome Tips (2015)^@^http://www.steeda.com/images/thumbnails/530/362/detailed/6/ford-racing-sport-mustang-ecoboost-axle-back-exhaust-chrome-tips-2015-161-m-5230-m4sc.jpg^@^161-M-5230-M4SC^@^<p>Ford Racing has partnered with industry leader Borla to offer the first in a series of Ford Racing by Borla exhaust systems for the new 2015 Mustang. This axle-back exhaust system is constructed from ultra-smooth mandrel bent 300-series stainless steel tubing that is designed and fit to Ford Racing specs. </p> <p>The 2.25&quot; axle-back exhaust pipe must be cut to install and clamp on the Ford Racing axle back mufflers. These tuned stainless steel mufflers with polished 4&quot; chrome-plated stainless steel tips not only sound great but look great too. </p> <p><strong>Product Benefits</strong> </p> <ul> <li>Aggressive muscle car sound</li> <li>Stainless steel construction</li> <li>4&quot; polished tips</li> <li>Direct bolt on</li> <li>Loud aggressive sound is 50-state drive-by noise legal</li> </ul><p>Time to install: <strong>About 1 1/2 Hours</strong></p><p>Level of difficulty: <strong>Tech Recommended</strong></p><p>Tools needed: <strong>Shop Tools</strong></p><p>Model year(s): <strong>2015</strong></p><p>Model(s): <strong>2.3L EcoBoost</strong></p><p>Transmission(s): <strong>Manual Automatic</strong></p>^@^Mustang^@^ 2.3L EcoBoost ^@^Mustang Exhaust^@^2015 ^@^Mustang Axle-Back Exhaust^@^099.95^
@848@^GAS - Steeda^@^GAS - Steeda^@848@^http://www.steeda.com/magnuson-tvs-2300-mustang-blue-supercharger-23-65-015-blue/^@^Steeda^@^Magnuson TVS 2300 Mustang Supercharger - Blue (11-14)^@^http://www.steeda.com/images/thumbnails/530/362/detailed/2/23-65-015-blue.jpg^@^23-65-015-BLUE^@^<p>Looking for instant power throughout the entire RPM range with OEM like reliability and drivebility? Look no further. </p> <p>Magnachargers supercharger system for the 2011-12 5.0L Mustang features an Eaton TVS 2300 supercharger. This unit delivers instant throttle response and boost over the entire RPM range. </p> <p>Magnacharger systems come complete with everything needed for installation including a cast aluminum intake manifold with intercooler core intercooler pump and heat exchanger factory &quot;push lock&quot; style connectors for the fuel system high capacity fuel injectors fuel rails and all the plumbing and related hardware. </p> <p>Looking to do the installation yourself? Magnacharger supplies a hand held computer programmer with the proper ECU calibration for the supercharger allowing the do it yourself enthusiast to install and properly program the system for a complete installation. </p> <p>Available in black or blue finishes. </p> <p><strong>Product Benefits</strong> </p> <ul> <li>Instant throttle response</li> <li>Instant boost at any RPM!</li> <li>Complete kit including ECU Calibration</li> </ul><p>Time to install: <strong>About 13 Hours</strong></p><p>Level of difficulty: <strong>Tech Recommended</strong></p><p>Tools needed: <strong>Basic Tools</strong></p><p>Model year(s): <strong>2014 2013 2012 2011</strong></p><p>Model(s): <strong>GT</strong></p><p>Transmission(s): <strong>Manual Automatic</strong></p>^@^Mustang^@^ GT ^@^Mustang Induction^@^2014 2013 2012 2011 ^@^Mustang Superchargers^@^994.95^
