@1118@^GAS - Steeda^@^GAS - Steeda^@1118@^http://www.steeda.com/dba-street-series-94-04-mustang-rear-driver-rotor-602-dba856sl/^@^Steeda^@^DBA Mustang Street Series Rotor - Rear Driver - 94-04 GT & V6^@^http://www.steeda.com/images/thumbnails/530/362/detailed/2/602-dba856sl.jpg^@^602-DBA856SL^@^<p>Want better braking for your GT500 without the expense of high dollar replacement calibers and rotors? Look no further these rotors are a direct replacement for the front rotors on a GT500 Mustang. They are OEM quality and feature machined slots for better cooling under extreme conditions. Rotors are sold as pairs and come with the factory finish. </p> <p><strong>Product Benefits</strong> </p> <ul> <li>Improved braking </li> <li>Perfect fit for the new GT500 </li> <li>OEM quality </li> <li>Easy installation </li> </ul><p>Time to install: <strong>About 1 Hour</strong></p><p>Level of difficulty: <strong>Tech Recommended</strong></p><p>Tools needed: <strong>Basic Tools</strong></p><p>Model year(s): <strong>2004 2003 2002 2001 2000 1999 1998 1997 1996 1995 1994</strong></p><p>Model(s): <strong>GT V6</strong></p><p>Transmission(s): <strong>Manual Automatic</strong></p>^@^Mustang^@^ GT V6 ^@^Mustang Brakes^@^2004 2003 2002 2001 2000 1999 1998 1997 1996 1995 1994 ^@^Mustang Brake Rotors^@^149.95^
