@1405@^GAS - Steeda^@^GAS - Steeda^@1405@^http://www.steeda.com/steeda-79-93-fox-body-mustang-aero-spoiler-307-0002/^@^Steeda^@^Steeda Fox Body Mustang Aero Spoiler - (79-93)^@^http://www.steeda.com/images/thumbnails/530/362/detailed/2/307-0002.jpg; http://www.steeda.com/images/thumbnails/530/362/detailed/3/307-0002-1.jpg; http://www.steeda.com/images/thumbnails/530/362/detailed/3/307-0002-2.jpg; http://www.steeda.com/images/thumbnails/530/362/detailed/3/307-0002-3.jpg^@^307-0002^@^<p>Steeda's trademark rear spoiler is the perfect blend of functional aerodynamics and distinctive styling. This unique spoiler extends the rear airfoil by several inches to trap high pressure air over the rear decklid increasing stability and control. But unlike most aftermarket spoilers our competition tested design increases downforce without increasing drag. </p> <p>The clean crisp styling is different enough to stand out in a crowd yet subtle enough to never go out of style. It's an easy 20 minute direct bolt-on for all 1987-1993 LX hatchbacks. It also fits all 1979-1993 hatchbacks including GT's with minor modifications. Wing comes with opening for 3rd brake light used on 1987-1993 LX and 1986 GT. </p> <p><strong>Product Benefits</strong> </p> <ul> <li>High speed down force</li> <li>Stylish design</li> </ul><p>Time to install: <strong>About 1 Hour</strong></p><p>Level of difficulty: <strong>Easy</strong></p><p>Tools needed: <strong>Basic Tools</strong></p><p>Model year(s): <strong>1993 1992 1991 1990 1989 1988 1987 1986 1985 1984 1983 1982 1981 1980 1979</strong></p><p>Model(s): <strong>5.0L V8 Cobra V6 2.3L</strong></p><p>Transmission(s): <strong>Manual Automatic</strong></p>^@^Mustang^@^ 5.0L V8 Cobra V6 2.3L ^@^Mustang Body Kits^@^1993 1992 1991 1990 1989 1988 1987 1986 1985 1984 1983 1982 1981 1980 1979 ^@^Mustang Rear Wings^@^44.95^
@1406@^GAS - Steeda^@^GAS - Steeda^@1406@^http://www.steeda.com/steeda-slide-style-captive-mustang-hood-pins-480-3037/^@^Steeda^@^Steeda Slide Style Captive Mustang Hood Pins - (79-10)^@^http://www.steeda.com/images/thumbnails/530/362/detailed/2/480-3037.jpg; http://www.steeda.com/images/thumbnails/530/362/detailed/3/480-3037-1.jpg^@^480-3037^@^<p>Recommended for any vehicle that will be operated at speeds in excess of 85 mph - we suspect that includes most folks surfing our site. You won't worry about dropping or losing any parts with these heavy-duty hood pins! </p> <p>The clevis pins always stay attached to the stainless steel retainer plates which get riveted or screwed to the hood surface. The 7/16 inch diameter steel hood pins measure 4 1/2 inches from the clevis pin opening to the bottom of the pin. The clevis pins are a full 1/4 inch diameter making these assemblies among the strongest available. Sold in pairs. </p> <p><strong>Product Benefits</strong> </p> <ul> <li>No lose wires to rub and wear your paint</li> <li>Secure fitting</li> <li>Easy to use</li> </ul><p>Time to install: <strong>About 1 Hour</strong></p><p>Level of difficulty: <strong>Easy</strong></p><p>Tools needed: <strong>Basic Tools</strong></p><p>Model year(s): <strong>2012 2011 2010 2009 2008 2007 2006 2005 2004 2003 2002 2001 2000 1999 1998 1997 1996 1995 1994 1993 1992 1991 1990 1989 1988 1987 1986 1985 1984 1983 1982 1981 1980 1979</strong></p><p>Model(s): <strong>5.0L V8 Bullitt Cobra Cobra R Mach 1 GT V6 GT500 Boss 2.3L</strong></p><p>Transmission(s): <strong>Manual Automatic</strong></p>^@^Mustang^@^ 5.0L V8 Bullitt Cobra Cobra R Mach 1 GT V6 GT500 Boss 2.3L ^@^Mustang Body Kits^@^2012 2011 2010 2009 2008 2007 2006 2005 2004 2003 2002 2001 2000 1999 1998 1997 1996 1995 1994 1993 1992 1991 1990 1989 1988 1987 1986 1985 1984 1983 1982 1981 1980 1979 ^@^Mustang Hood Accessories^@49.95
@1407@^GAS - Steeda^@^GAS - Steeda^@1407@^http://www.steeda.com/steeda-mustang-hood-strut-kit-555-0684/^@^Steeda^@^Steeda Mustang Hood Strut Kit - 05-14^@^http://www.steeda.com/images/thumbnails/530/362/detailed/2/555-0684.jpg; http://www.steeda.com/images/thumbnails/530/362/detailed/3/555-0684-1.jpg^@^555-0684^@^<p>Our Steeda Bolt on Hood Strut Kit is designed to be a simple bolt on using the stock hood for 2005-2014 Mustangs. </p> <p>This bolt on hood strut kit uses an existing hole on the factory hood to secure the hood mount fender brackets complete the opposite end allowing the 2 supplied hood struts to just snap into place making it a complete bolt on installation with no drilling required. </p> <p><strong>Note:</strong> Will not work with aftermarket hoods the hood attachment end only attaches to an existing hole in the Ford OEM hood only. These hood struts include a 1-year warranty. </p> <p>For all aftermarket hoods we recommend our Steeda hood strut kits with billet attachment brackets. </p> <p><strong>Product Benefits</strong> </p> <ul> <li>Simple bolt on installation</li> <li>Works with factory original hoods only</li> <li>No drilling or cutting needed</li> </ul><p>Time to install: <strong>About 1 Hour</strong></p><p>Level of difficulty: <strong>Easy</strong></p><p>Tools needed: <strong>Basic Tools</span> </div> </div> <div style=with:100%

