@1414@^GAS - Steeda^@^GAS - Steeda^@1414@^http://www.steeda.com/classic-design-concepts-mustang-light-bar-067-110001/^@^Steeda^@^Classic Design Concepts Mustang Light Bar - Gray (05-14)^@^http://www.steeda.com/images/thumbnails/530/362/detailed/1/067-110001.jpg; http://www.steeda.com/images/thumbnails/530/362/detailed/2/067-110001-1.jpg^@^067-110001^@^<p>Designed right for easy installation and a perfect fit. The light bar has been shaped to fit the curves and natural lines of the vehicle to provide a factory looking fit and finish. The high mounted LED brake light provides added safety with the highly visible light. </p> <p>The factory top effortlessly fits over the light bar with no interference and the Classic Light Bar does not interfere with any original factory functions. The light bar is constructed of a sturdy 1 ¼” round steel tube with a 1/8” wall thickness. The polyurethane mold is then wrapped in vinyl. The bar simple bolts to the B pillar for a sturdy mount and also stiffens the body. Installation can be done in about 4 hours and complete instructions are provided. </p> <p><strong>Note:</strong> Although constructed with a steel bar this part is not meant to provide roll over protection. </p> <p><strong>Product Benefits</strong> </p> <ul> <li>Quality OE fit and finish</li> <li>Stylish design</li> <li>Built in LED </li> </ul><p>Time to install: <strong>About 4 Hours</strong></p><p>Level of difficulty: <strong>Tech Recommended</strong></p><p>Tools needed: <strong>Basic Tools</strong></p><p>Model year(s): <strong>2014 2013 2012 2011 2010 2009 2008 2007 2006 2005</strong></p><p>Model(s): <strong>GT V6 GT500</strong></p><p>Transmission(s): <strong>Manual Automatic</strong></p>^@^Mustang^@^ GT V6 GT500 ^@^Mustang Body Kits^@^2014 2013 2012 2011 2010 2009 2008 2007 2006 2005 ^@^Mustang Light Bars^@^634.95^
@1415@^GAS - Steeda^@^GAS - Steeda^@1415@^http://www.steeda.com/steeda-mustang-hood-struts-555-0651/^@^Steeda^@^Steeda Billet Mustang Hood Strut Kit - (05-14)^@^http://www.steeda.com/images/thumbnails/530/362/detailed/2/555-0651.jpg; http://www.steeda.com/images/thumbnails/530/362/detailed/3/555-0651-1.jpg^@^555-0651^@^<p>Steeda's billet hood strut kit is the perfect way to dress up the engine bay of your Stang. Made out of billet 6061 aluminum they are light weight and come engraved with the Steeda name. </p> <p>OEM quality gas struts are included in this kit. Steeda has engineered this kit to fit and function better than the other kits on the market. There are clearance reliefs in the brackets for the washer fluid hose and a rubber bump stop on the underside to protect the paint on the underside of your hood. </p> <p>No drilling or modifications required for installation. These hood struts include a 1-year warranty. </p> <p><strong>Product Benefits</strong> </p> <ul> <li>More room to work on your motor in the front of the engine bay</li> <li>Also more room on the sides then competitors kits</li> <li>Lightweight billet aluminum and stylish with the Steeda logo or available plain </li> <li>No drilling or permanent modifications required for installation like other brands</li> <li>Hood struts meet/exceed OE standards</li> </ul><p>Time to install: <strong>About 1 Hour</strong></p><p>Level of difficulty: <strong>Easy</strong></p><p>Tools needed: <strong>Basic Tools</span> </div> </div> <div style=with:100%

