@1943@^GAS - Steeda^@^GAS - Steeda^@1943@^http://www.steeda.com/magnaflow-mustang-competition-axle-back-exhaust-263-15596/^@^Steeda^@^Magnaflow Mustang Competition Axle-back Exhaust (11-14 V6)^@^http://www.steeda.com/images/thumbnails/530/362/detailed/5/image12398.jpg^@^263-15596^@^<p>Experience the aggressive and impressive sound of Magnaflow's Competition Axle-back for your 2011-2014 Mustang V6. </p> <p>The Magnaflow Competition Axle-back has a straight through muffler delete design for minimal restriction that improves exhaust flow sound and power. </p> <p>The Magnaflow Competition axle-back exhaust system features 2.5&quot; stainless steel mandrel bent tubing for long life and dual 4&quot; polished stainless steel tips. </p> <p>This muffler delete axle-back will bolt right up without any modification. Installation instructions are included. </p> <p><strong>Product Benefits</strong> </p> <ul> <li><span style=background-color: initial

