@1944@^GAS - Steeda^@^GAS - Steeda^@1944@^http://www.steeda.com/ford-racing-sport-catback-mustang-ecoboost-exhaust-chrome-tips-2015-161-m-5200-m4sc/^@^Steeda^@^Ford Racing Sport Catback Mustang Ecoboost Exhaust-Chrome Tips (2015)^@^http://www.steeda.com/images/thumbnails/530/362/detailed/6/ford-racing-sport-catback-mustang-exhaust-chrome-tips-2015-161-m-5200-m8sc(2)_e2fo-yi.jpg; http://www.steeda.com/images/thumbnails/530/326/detailed/6/M-5230-M8SConcars_uftf-z2.jpg^@^161-M-5200-M4SC^@^<p>Ford Racing has partnered with industry leader Borla® to offer the first in a series of Ford Racing by Borla® exhaust systems for the new 2015 Mustang. This cat-back exhaust system is constructed from ultra-smooth mandrel bent 300-series stainless steel tubing that is designed and fit to Ford Racing specs. </p> <p>This 2.25&quot; cat-back exhaust system bolts directly to the factory catalytic converter making your Mustang 100% emission compliant and also providing you with performance sound. These tuned stainless steel mufflers with polished 4&quot; chrome-plated stainless steel tips not only sound great but look great too. </p> <p><strong>Please Note: </strong>This Ford Racing Sport Cat-back Exhaust System is 49 state drive by noise legal not intended for use in the state of California. </p> <p><strong>Product Benefits</strong> </p> <ul> <li>Approximately 20 lbs lighter than the factory cat-back system</li> <li>Bolts to stock catalytic converter</li> <li>4&quot; chrome-plated stainless steel tip</li> <li>Aggressive muscle car sound</li> </ul><p>Time to install: <strong>About 2 1/2 Hours</strong></p><p>Level of difficulty: <strong>Tech Recommended</strong></p><p>Tools needed: <strong>Basic Tools</strong></p><p>Model year(s): <strong>2015</strong></p><p>Model(s): <strong>2.3L EcoBoost</strong></p><p>Transmission(s): <strong>Manual Automatic</strong></p>^@^Mustang^@^ 2.3L EcoBoost ^@^Mustang Exhaust^@^2015 ^@^Mustang Cat-Back Exhaust^@^1599.95^
@1945@^GAS - Steeda^@^GAS - Steeda^@1945@^http://www.steeda.com/bbk-off-road-mustang-x-pipe-for-use-w-long-tube-headers-07-10-gt500-035-1651/^@^Steeda^@^BBK Off-Road Mustang X-Pipe - for use w/ Long Tube Headers (07-10 GT500)^@^http://www.steeda.com/images/thumbnails/530/530/detailed/5/bbk-off-road-mustang-x-pipe-for-use-w-long-tube-headers-07-10-gt500-035-1651.jpg^@^035-1651^@^<p>The X-pipe from BBK features CNC mandrel bent aluminized tubing that will ensure maximum durability flow and horsepower in your performance machine. This is a large 2-3/4&quot; Aluminized Off-Road X-Pipe specifically designed for all 2007 2008 2009 and 2010 Shelby GT500s using BBK Long Tube Headers. </p> <p>BBK has dyno-tested this off road X-pipe in-house and has shown solid horsepower gains of 12 to 25 horsepower. There are 02 sensor extensions included for the new repositioning this X-pipe will create. A unique feature the high-flow X junction design delivers unrestricted flow to maximize the potential of Ford's late model high performance engines. </p> <p><strong>Note:</strong> Federal and several state and provincial laws prohibit the removal modification or rendering inoperative of any part that affects emissions or safety on motor vehicles used on public streets or highways. Steeda Autosports assumes no liability for any violations arising out of any federal state or provincial emissions or safety requirements on motor vehicles arising out of the customer's modifications and/or use of Steeda products. It is the responsibility of the customer to determine if their modified vehicle complies with applicable laws. </p> <p><strong>Warning:</strong> This part has been designed and is intended for off-road application only. Installation of this part on a vehicle that is driven on public roads may violate U.S. and Canadian laws and regulations. </p> <p><strong>Product Benefits</strong> </p> <ul> <li>Aggressive muscle car sound</li> <li>Increased horsepower and torque</li> <li>Made in the USA</li> </ul> <p><strong>Note:</strong> For use with BBK Long Tube Full Length Headers 035-16490 or 035-16495 </p> <p>This limited warranty is the only express warranty applicable to Steeda Autosports products. Other rights may arise or vary from state to state in the United States. Steeda is not responsible for any time for which you may lose the use of your vehicle any inconvenience you might be caused the loss of your transportation or any part thereof or any other incidental or consequential damages you may have. </p><p>Time to install: <strong>About 2 Hours</strong></p><p>Level of difficulty: <strong>Tech Recommended</strong></p><p>Tools needed: <strong>Shop Tools</strong></p><p>Model year(s): <strong>2010 2009 2008 2007</strong></p><p>Model(s): <strong><br /><br /> <span class=install-box-name-title">Transmission(s)</span><br /> Manual Automatic</strong></p>^@^Mustang^@^ ^@^Mustang Exhaust^@^2010 2009 2008 2007 ^@^Mustang X-Pipes^@325.95

