@1949@^GAS - Steeda^@^GAS - Steeda^@1949@^http://www.steeda.com/steeda-mustang-suspension-package-555-2123/^@^Steeda^@^Steeda G/Trac Mustang Suspension Package - Stage 1 (94-97 GT & 96-97 Cobra)^@^http://www.steeda.com/images/thumbnails/530/362/detailed/1/555-2123.jpg; http://www.steeda.com/images/thumbnails/530/362/detailed/3/555-2123-1.jpg; http://www.steeda.com/images/thumbnails/530/362/detailed/3/555-2123-2.jpg; http://www.steeda.com/images/thumbnails/530/362/detailed/3/555-2123-3.jpg; http://www.steeda.com/images/thumbnails/530/362/detailed/3/555-2123-4.jpg^@^555-2123^@^<p>Steeda's G/Trac Suspension Systems include everything needed to build an awesome handling car with excellent street manners. Steeda's G/Trac suspension components are proven components tested through decades of experience gained from street and racetrack testing. </p> <p>Each stage provides an outstanding improvement in performance and a well balanced car at the end of each stage. This means you do not have to do each stage in numerical order to achieve improvements. Each stage can be done individually at any time as your budget or upgrade needs dictate. </p> <p>Steeda’s Stage 1 suspension package lays the foundation for proper handling and builds a base for any future modifications by addressing three essential elements needed for performance. </p> <ul> <li>Sport Lowering Springs lower the center of gravity and reduce body roll while maintaining the great ride quality Steeda springs are known for. </li> <li>Strut Tower and lower G/Trac braces stiffen the body structure to stabilize the suspension during hard cornering and reduce body shake and rattles. Steeda G/Trac bars are included with 86-93 cars. 94+ have factory G/Trac style bars so our kits do not include them. </li> <li>Caster Camber Plates allow you to set proper alignment and improve caster geometry while eliminating suspension “slop” at the top of the strut tower. Improved caster gives you straighter highway tracking with less wander and better self centering steering feel. Increased caster also gives you better tire contact patch area during braking or better more consistent braking performance.</li> </ul><p>Time to install: <strong>About 7 Hours</strong></p><p>Level of difficulty: <strong>Tech Recommended</strong></p><p>Tools needed: <strong>Shop Tools</strong></p><p>Model year(s): <strong>1997 1996 1995 1994</strong></p><p>Model(s): <strong>Cobra GT</strong></p><p>Transmission(s): <strong>Manual Automatic</strong></p>^@^Mustang^@^ Cobra GT ^@^Mustang Suspension^@^1997 1996 1995 1994 ^@^Mustang Suspension Packages^@^29.95^
@1950@^GAS - Steeda^@^GAS - Steeda^@1950@^http://www.steeda.com/steeda-v6-mustang-axle-back-exhaust-040-130100/^@^Steeda^@^Steeda Mustang Axle-Back Exhaust (05-09 V6)^@^http://www.steeda.com/images/thumbnails/530/362/detailed/2/040-130100.jpg^@^040-130100^@^<p>A less restrictive exhaust path enhances performance and this axle-back Steeda system features an authoritative tone direct bolt-in installation. Also includes a lifetime warranty stainless steel construction with polished tip. </p> <p><strong>Product Benefits</strong> </p> <ul> <li>Less restrictive than stock exhaust </li> <li>Enhances performance</li> <li>Lifetime warranty</li> <li>Does not void vehicle warranty </li> </ul><p>Time to install: <strong>About 45 Minutes</strong></p><p>Level of difficulty: <strong>Tech Recommended</strong></p><p>Tools needed: <strong>Basic Tools</strong></p><p>Model year(s): <strong>2009 2008 2007 2006 2005</strong></p><p>Model(s): <strong>V6</strong></p><p>Transmission(s): <strong>Manual Automatic</strong></p>^@^Mustang^@^ V6 ^@^2005-2010 Exhaust^@^2009 2008 2007 2006 2005 ^@^2005-2010 Axle-Back Exhaust^@^304.95^
@1951@^GAS - Steeda^@^GAS - Steeda^@1951@^http://www.steeda.com/bbk-varitune-mustang-axle-back-exhaust-stainless-steel-035-41005/^@^Steeda^@^BBK Varitune Mustang Axle-Back Exhaust Stainless Steel (05-10 GT)^@^http://www.steeda.com/images/thumbnails/530/362/detailed/5/cbk68_1.74.jpg^@^035-41005^@^<p>This BBK Mustang Axle-Back Exhaust system features BBK's patented tunable Varitune performance mufflers that allow you to change from a mellow three chamber exhaust sound to a more aggressive straight-through exhaust sound. </p> <p>BBK Varitune performance mufflers utilize an internal &quot;Adjustable Power Valve&quot;. When in the closed position the valve blocks the exhaust flow forcing it through all three chambers of the muffler for a classic mellow sound. When in the open position the valve bypasses the chambers allowing it to follow a straight-through muffler path for a rich throaty exhaust note. So now you can open it up for the track and close it down for a roadtrip. </p> <p>This BBK Performance Axle-Back exhaust system features Varitune chambered mufflers that end with 4&quot; polished 304 stainless tips for impressive looks and sound. The tips exit in the stock locations so no modification to the rear bumper cover is required. </p> <p><strong>Product Benefits</strong> </p> <ul> <li><span style=background-color: initial

