@1955@^GAS - Steeda^@^GAS - Steeda^@1955@^http://www.steeda.com/magnalfow-mustang-axle-back-exhaust-263-15889/^@^Steeda^@^Magnaflow Mustang Axle-Back Exhaust (05-09 V6)^@^http://www.steeda.com/images/thumbnails/530/362/detailed/1/263-15889.jpg^@^263-15889^@^<p>Magnaflow offers two options for S197 GT owners looking to upgrade their exhaust system. You can replace everything from the catalytic converters back with their Cat-Back System (above) or you can save a little cash and make installation easier too with the Axle-Back System (middle). </p> <p>Improve performance get the sound of power for your pony car! V6 owners also upgrade from the axle back with our latest addition. All feature polished tips for a custom look. </p> <p><strong>Product Specifications</strong> </p> <ul> <li><strong>Material:</strong> 100% Stainless Steel</li> <li><strong>Tubing O.D. Size:</strong> 2.5in.</li> <li><strong>System Type:</strong> Cat-Back</li> <li><strong>TIP O.D. Size:</strong> 3.5in.</li> <li><strong>TIP Quantity:</strong> 2</li> <li><strong>Single/Dual:</strong> Dual</li> <li><strong>Exit Position:</strong> DUAL SPLIT REAR EXIT</li> </ul> <p><strong>Product Benefits</strong> </p> <ul> <li>Choose Cat-Back or Axle-Back system </li> <li>Improve Performance </li> <li>Sound of Power! </li> </ul><p>Time to install: <strong>About 1 1/2 Hours</strong></p><p>Level of difficulty: <strong>Tech Recommended</strong></p><p>Tools needed: <strong>Basic Tools</span> </div> </div> <div style=with:100%

