@2027@^GAS - Steeda^@^GAS - Steeda^@2027@^http://www.steeda.com/bbk-off-road-mustang-x-pipe-for-use-w-long-tube-headers-11-14-v6-035-1462/^@^Steeda^@^BBK Off-Road Mustang X-Pipe for use w/ Long Tube Headers (11-14) V6^@^http://www.steeda.com/images/thumbnails/530/530/detailed/5/bbk-off-road-mustang-x-pipe-for-use-w-long-tube-headers-11-14-v6-035-1462.jpg^@^035-1462^@^<p>BBK Performance X pipes will give your Mustang a track ready aggressive sound. BBK's unique die stamped performance Xtracter center X section ensures maximum flow and horsepower. </p> <p>This BBK x-pipe is specifically designed to be used with BBK's 1642 Series long tube headers. </p> <p>BBK's X-pipes use a 2.75&quot; diameter CNC mandrel bent aluminized tubing and a merged X crossover to improve flow. It also features OEM style hangers that attach in the stock locations for easy installation. </p> <p>This BBK Shorty Off-road X-Pipe is specifically designed to fit the 2011-2014 Mustang V6's with BBK Long-Tube Headers installed. </p> <p><strong>Warning: </strong>This part has been designed and is intended for off-road application only. Installation of this part on a vehicle that is driven on public roads may violate U.S. and Canadian laws and regulations. </p> <p><strong>Product Benefits</strong> </p> <ul> <li>Aggressive muscle car sound</li> <li>Improved exhaust flow</li> <li>Fits BBK's 1642 Series Long tube headers</li> <li>For off-road track use</li> </ul> <p>Note: Federal and several state and provincial laws prohibit the removal modification or rendering inoperative of any part that affects emissions or safety on motor vehicles used on public streets or highways. Steeda Autosports assumes no liability for any violations arising out of any federal state or provincial emissions or safety requirements on motor vehicles arising out of the customer’s modifications and/or use of Steeda products. It is the responsibility of the customer to determine if their modified vehicle complies with applicable laws. </p> <p>This limited warranty is the only express warranty applicable to Steeda Autosports products. Other rights may arise or vary from state to state in the United States. Steeda is not responsible for any time for which you may lose the use of your vehicle any inconvenience you might be caused the loss of your transportation or any part thereof or any other incidental or consequential damages you may have. </p><p>Time to install: <strong>About 2 Hours</strong></p><p>Level of difficulty: <strong>Tech Recommended</strong></p><p>Tools needed: <strong>Basic Tools</strong></p><p>Model year(s): <strong>2014 2013 2012 2011</strong></p><p>Model(s): <strong>V6</strong></p><p>Transmission(s): <strong>Manual Automatic</strong></p>^@^Mustang^@^ V6 ^@^Mustang Exhaust^@^2014 2013 2012 2011 ^@^Mustang X-Pipes^@^225.95^
@2028@^GAS - Steeda^@^GAS - Steeda^@2028@^http://www.steeda.com/steeda-mustang-triple-pass-heat-exchanger-555-3707/^@^Steeda^@^Steeda Triple Pass Mustang Heat Exchanger With Fans (05-12)^@^http://www.steeda.com/images/thumbnails/530/362/detailed/2/555-3707.jpg^@^555-3707^@^<p>When we set out to make our own heat exchanger for the GT500 we set out to achieve the absolute highest cooling capacity available. We have achieved just that with our 07-12 GT500 heat exchanger. Our <strong>triple</strong> pass design is the only one of its kind on the market all others are single or double pass units. </p> <p>Many competitive units are advertised using outside dimensions that are passed off as actual cooling area dimensions meaning a unit being shown with 2 inches of thickness outside but actually only has 1 1/4 inches for the actual core itself making it hard to make true comparisons. Our true core thickness coming in at 1.7 inches is larger than any other dual fan heat exchanger on the market. </p> <p>Our triple pass design along with the largest true core thickness and powerful dual 800+ CFM fans allowed us to achieve 18% more heat rejection than the closest competitor making this heat exchanger the superior choice for all uses including street use and in particular road racing where long periods under constant boost generates constant heat that needs to be dissipated. </p> <p>In addition we went the extra mile and designed a true plug and play harness for the wiring of the fans requiring no wiring work. No cutting splicing or soldering of any kind will be needed making it is truly plug and play. Our heat exchanger is an easy direct bolt on replacement that is manufactured from high quality aluminum and fully TIG welded. It is also fully bushed for isolation from vibration which can cause premature failure of the unit. </p> <p>Pair this heat exchanger with <a href=http://www.steeda.com/ford-racing-gt500-mustang-intercooler-upgrade-161-m-6775-msvt/">Ford Racing's Upgraded GT500 intercooler</a> for the ultimate supercharger cooling upgrade! </p> <p>This unit also works with 2005+ GT models with Whipple and Magnuson Superchargers with minor modification. </p> <p><strong>Product Benefits</strong> </p> <ul> <li>TRIPLE Pass Heat Exchanger - others are only single or dual</li> <li>Plug and play fan wiring harness - no cutting or splicing</li> <li>18% more heat rejection than closest competitive unit</li> <li>A must if you road race your GT500 and a superior unit for street use</li> </ul><p>Time to install: <strong>About 5 Hours</strong></p><p>Level of difficulty: <strong>Tech Recommended</strong></p><p>Tools needed: <strong>Basic Tools</span> </div> </div> <div style="with:100%

